Bf4 Bd6 {Has been a common way to take advantage of this move order.} (11...
Qa5+ $1 {is probably simplest as the variations with White going c2-c3-c4 are
good for Black (see previous file)} 12. Bd2 Bb4 13. c3 Be7 14. c4 Qc7 15. O-O-O
