21. c4 (21. Bb4 Nce4 (21... Nd3+) 22. Bxe7+ Rxe7 23. Qxh6+ Rg7 24. Qh8+ Rg8 25.
Rxg8+ Nxg8 26. Ng6+ Kf7 27. Ne5+ Kf8 28. Ng6+ Kf7 29. Ne5+ Kf8 {1/2-1/2 (29)
