Gg8f6]}) 3... dxe4 4. Nc3 Nf6 5. Nge2 (5. Qe2 Bf5) 5... Bf5 6. Ng3 e6 7. Qe2
Nbd7 8. Ngxe4 Be7 9. O-O-O a5 $1 {0-1 (48) Reprintsev,A (2428)-Dreev,A (2690)
